import { Grid } from '@material-ui/core';
import React from 'react';

function calc() {
	return (
		<Grid
			item
			container
			alignItems="center"
			className="calc-cont"
			justify="end"
			direction="column"
			style={{ background: 'red' }}
		>
			<Grid item container xs="3" style={{ background: 'green' }}>
				<Grid item>7</Grid>
				<Grid item>8</Grid>
				<Grid item>9</Grid>
				<Grid item>\</Grid>
			</Grid>
			<Grid item container xs="10">
				<Grid item>4</Grid>
				<Grid item>5</Grid>
				<Grid item>6</Grid>
				<Grid item>x</Grid>
			</Grid>
			<Grid item container xs="10">
				<Grid item>1</Grid>
				<Grid item>2</Grid>
				<Grid item>3</Grid>
				<Grid item>-</Grid>
			</Grid>
			<Grid item container xs="10">
				<Grid item>0</Grid>
				<Grid item>.</Grid>
				<Grid item>=</Grid>
				<Grid item>+</Grid>
			</Grid>
		</Grid>
	);
}

export default calc;
